Package: arsampler
Type: Package
Title: Perform Acceptance-Rejection Sampling
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Enggelin", "Wongkar",
      email = "enggelin.wongkar@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This is a package to help perform the acceptance-rejection sampling without having to code the entire algorithm itself.
    The current version of this package can only accept a proposal densities from pre-defined templates while the user can define their own target densities.
